                            </figure>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="testimonial-sec">
    <div class="sec-container bg-invert">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="sec-title col-lg-12 text-center">
                <h2 class="txt-title-invert">What People Say</h2>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-9 col-centered text-center">
                <div id="testimonial-carousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
                    <div class="carousel-inner col-lg-8 col-centered">
                        <div class="carousel-item active">
                            <div class="single-testimonial-item">
                                <p>"<span>I have searched for a long time for the great ring (the precious one), and now after so much wars I have finally found it in Jewellis! My precious!</span>"</p>
                                <h3 class="client-name">- <span>Gollum</span> -</h3>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <div class="single-testimonial-item">
                                <p>"<span>I've collected so many rings and I just can't seem to have enough, after purchsing the Jewellis gold ring I finally feel whole.</span>"</p>
                                <h3 class="client-name">- <span>Sonic</span> -</h3>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <div class="single-testimonial-item">
                                <p>"<span>I've searched all over the galaxy for the perfect stones, and even sacrificed the things I love the most for them. The best one, I found in Jewellis.</span>"</p>
                                <h3 class="client-name">- <span>Thanos</span> -</h3>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#testimonial-carousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
                        <span class="icon icon-arrow-left15 h1" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
                    </a>
                    <a class="carousel-control-next" href="#testimonial-carousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
                        <span class="icon icon-arrow-right16 h1" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="newsletter-sec">
    <div class="sec-container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="sec-title col-lg-12 text-center">
                <h2>Join The Newsletter</h2>
                <p>Get Updates On Awesome Jewelry!</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row">
            <form action="" method="post" id="subscribe-form">
                <div class="i-txt-with-btn-wrapper mob-break px-5">
                    <input type="email" name="email" id="sub-email" class="i-txt bg-input-txt font-italic" placeholder="Enter your email here..." required />
                    <button type="submit" class="btn outline-primary">Subscribe</button>
                </div>
                <div id="sub-result"></div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
